next time i 'll aim for the heart ( french : la prochaine fois je viserai le cœur ) is a 2014 french thriller film written and directed by cédric anger .   it was adapted from the novel un assassin au-dessus de tout soupçon by yvan stefanovitch .   set in 1970s oise , france , it tells the true story of alain lamare , a gendarme who was later revealed to be a horrific serial killer .